						               													<description>Schlag den Raab: Das Quiz is a board game based on a German TV show in which players have to compete in different challenges. In contrast to earlier Schlag den Raab games, these challenges are all card-based with no dexterity elements; the game includes more than two thousand quiz questions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The thirty challenge categories include guessing words whose letters have been jumbled, counting letters in words, spelling words backwards, guessing which movie a quote is from, mental arithmetic, drawing a song (so that others can guess which song it is), humming songs, and locating places (Germany/EU/world) on a map. The challenges are chosen randomly, and the players can score points in all of these games. After the predetermined number of challenges &amp;ndash; five for a 45-50 minute game, ten for a 75-90 minute game, fifteen for a 100-120 minute game &amp;ndash; has been played, the player/team with the highest score wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Can be combined with&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Schlag den Raab: Das Spiel&amp;#10;    Schlag den Raab: Das 2. Spiel&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
